'''Haven's Water''' was a tavern on [[Port Haven/Legends|Port Haven]] operated by the [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] [[Mister Mxil]]. It was a warmly lit building made of stone, and served beverages made with natural ingredients [[Gender/Legends|he]] found in the nearby [[Jungle/Legends|jungle]]. Over the entrance, there was an empty [[Water/Legends|water]] skin hanging to show that it was a place for thirsty customers.<ref name="Platt's Starport Guide">''[[Platt's Starport Guide]]''</ref>

